{"page":1,"results":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":2134310,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Michele Mally","original_name":"Michele Mally","popularity":0.3017,"profile_path":"/pxCkqpUfADUfLiRtOLeeMTJFt4H.jpg","known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/x1QiDczr7XQ3mgWeKbNjW1sUST5.jpg","id":550159,"title":"Klimt & Schiele: Eros and Psyche","original_title":"Klimt & Schiele: Eros e Psiche","overview":"1918. As the roar of the First World War cannons is dying out, in Vienna, the heart of Central Europe, a golden age comes to an end. The Austro-Hungarian Empire is beginning to disintegrate. On the night of October 31st, in the bed of his home, Egon Schiele dies, one of the 20 million deaths caused by the Spanish flu. He dies looking at the invisible evil in the face, in the only he can do: painting it. He is 28 years old. Only a few months earlier, the main hall of the Secession building had welcomed his works: 19 oil paintings and 29 drawings. His first successful exhibition, a celebration of a new painting idea that portrays the restlessness and desires of mankind.A few months earlier, his teacher and friend Gustav Klimt had died. From the turn of the century, he had fundamentally changed the feeling of art and founded a new group: the Secession.","poster_path":"/liJ3s6w2mSRGX8byv5MQf9fafqd.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"it","genre_ids":[99,36],"popularity":0.266,"release_date":"2018-10-22","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.0,"vote_count":32},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/t2A7qKSj7Mt73A6q33BXIIL0YBQ.jpg","id":875405,"title":"Venice: Infinitely Avant-Garde","original_title":"Venezia - Infinita avanguardia","overview":"1600 years after its legendary foundation, Venice continues to be unique: the urban environment, made of stone, earth, and water, and for its legendary history. But, above all, Venice is unique for its identity as a city of oxymorons, holding together opposing DNA in a formidable contradiction: the allure of decadence, and the frenzy of the avant-garde. VENEZIA-INFINITA AVANGUARDIA is a labyrinth of stories, works of art, palaces, celebrities of social and cultural life, places, extravagances, and traditions. It's a sensory experience made of lights, water, and music. Beside connections and suggestions, testaments flow by of art historians, urbanists, sociologists, philosophers, curators, musicians, writers, journalists, artists, and our contemporaries.","poster_path":"/tyW8YDfCXcRctSA4xJln6Fi66q3.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"it","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.226,"release_date":"2021-10-11","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":6.9,"vote_count":8},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/kADH6OlNaXCcnb9eakMZw2fWEhh.jpg","id":619401,"title":"Hermitage: The Power of Art","original_title":"Ermitage: il potere dell'arte","overview":"","poster_path":"/uk4LMVIoetOgAYxzkHmEBEbs3c4.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"it","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.1505,"release_date":"2019-10-21","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.3,"vote_count":6}]}],"total_pages":1,"total_results":1}